ActPoverty Reduction Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Employment and Social Development To Be the Minister for the Purposes of the Poverty Reduction Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2020-123 of March 9, 2020; and (2) designating the Minister of EMPLOYMENT AND SOCIAL DEVELOPMENT, a member of the King's Privy Council for Canada, to be the Minister for the purposes of the POVERTY REDUCTION ACT.
